By: @jacobandco for @universalpictures

node.text:
Matching Rolls-Royce Ghost x Cullinan 🐼 #millionairesurroundings

By: @deuiteinden

#rollsroyce #rollsroycecullinan #rollsroyceghost #rolls #rollsroycephantom #phantom #luxurycars #luxurylife #drivetastefully

@jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon Pavé 💎

The partnership between Jacob & Co and Bugatti has brought to market some of the most exquisite timepieces. This being one of them 😍

The Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon Pavé’s heart replicates the W16 Chiron engine block; by pushing the right crown of the watch, the pistons pump up and down driven by the crankshaft, reenacting the movements of the pistons within the engine.

Truly an incredible feat of watchmaking to match a truly record braking hypercar.

By: @jacobandco for @bugatti | #millionairesurroundings #jacobandco

#luxury #luxurylifestyle #bugatti #watch #watchesofinstagram #watches #jewellery #jewelry #limitededition
